{"tid":1040254,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我個仔岩岩出世 我姓陳  老婆話要改單字一個皮","createTime":"2019-02-28T03:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T17:44:35.000Z","uid":150912,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"42a4e154ecaf60c6ddfe44ebeb3c4b86df8c1382","tid":1040254,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"我個仔幾日前出世<br />\n我同老婆依兩日鬧得好勁<br />\n因為佢話要改個仔個名做陳皮<br />\n我開頭以為佢講笑<br />\n點知佢認真<br />\n仲解釋我聽話陳皮係一種放得愈來愈有價值的野<br />\n佢話想個仔愈大愈有內涵<br />\n唔好愈老愈冇用  變左廢老咁  反而要更有智慧同價值<br />\n我話咁樣個仔會俾人笑<br />\n佢話岩呀陳皮係岩岩曬的時候都係冇咩香味<br />\n俾人笑係磨練  等於被陽光沐浴的過程<br />\n到佢大左自然唔會再有人笑 反而得到磨練而更加堅強<br />\n我完全唔夠佢講 連雙親都俾佢講到覺得陳皮係好名<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日約左老死食糖水宵夜順便呻下  見到個menu有陳皮紅豆沙時  我個心即刻拿住拿住  差d喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：好愛我老婆"},{"pid":"89e022e1062aa01476c0f510ef36762fb4584567","tid":1040254,"uid":134091,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"同catgirl生？"},{"pid":"ce3ba2755b9c5caf9bd0ac0e929cffd832af0f60","tid":1040254,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"a12d9c983b47b8ee4ee14f552426e7db971acb9d","tid":1040254,"uid":211461,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"天生校園/職場欺凌對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e72f5a1a95d69404094d784582b6eefde5fdbfc","tid":1040254,"uid":208375,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"英文名champion<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0378c5bdb0a1a73753ee0e57d1eb127a7f627731","tid":1040254,"uid":226524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:29:50.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"539855a8ccd37a59685eb5cd5b9478eac746fa86","tid":1040254,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike"